column2: SELECT top #  p.objID,p.skyVersion,p.run,p.rerun,p.camcol,p.field,p.obj,p.mode,p.nChild,p.type,p.probPSF,p.insideMask,p.flags,p.psfMag_u,p.psfMag_g,p.psfMag_r,p.psfMag_i,p.psfMag_z,p.psfMagErr_u,p.psfMagErr_g,p.psfMagErr_r,p.psfMagErr_i,p.psfMagErr_z,p.petroMag_u,p.petroMag_g,p.petroMag_r,p.petroMag_i,p.petroMag_z,p.petroMagErr_u,p.petroMagErr_g,p.petroMagErr_r,p.petroMagErr_i,p.petroMagErr_z,p.petroR5#_r,p.petroR9#_r,p.modelMag_u,p.modelMag_g,p.modelMag_r,p.modelMag_i,p.modelMag_z,p.modelMagErr_u,p.modelMagErr_g,p.modelMagErr_r,p.modelMagErr_i,p.modelMagErr_z,p.mRrCc_r,p.mRrCcErr_r,p.lnLStar_r,p.lnLExp_r,p.lnLDeV_r,p.ra as ra_p,p.dec as dec_p,p.cx as cx_p,p.cy as cy_p,p.cz as cz_p,p.extinction_u,p.extinction_g,p.extinction_r,p.extinction_i,p.extinction_z,p.htmID as htmID_p,p.fieldID,p.specObjID as specObjID_p, SQRT(p.mRrCc_r/#) as size,s.specObjID as specObjID_s,s.bestObjID  FROM  PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestObjID=p.objID and s.specObjID=p.specObjID WHERE  p.mode=#  AND p.type=#  AND p.ra BETWEEN # and #  AND p.dec BETWEEN # and #  AND p.petroRad_u># and p.petroRad_g># and p.petroRad_r># and p.petroRad_i># and p.petroRad_z>#  AND p.petroRadErr_g>#  AND p.petroMag_g BETWEEN # and #  AND s.z<=# ORDER BY  p.objID
